{#
    Rich Text Block (Theme Component: home.rich-text)
    ====================================================
    Free-form merchant-authored HTML (WYSIWYG field) — a "Custom Section"
    building block for marketing copy, store policies highlights, seasonal
    messaging, etc. that doesn't warrant a dedicated component.

    | component.title         | string|null | optional heading             |
    | component.content       | string      | plain text (textarea field)  |
    | component.center_align  | bool        | center the text block        |

    `component.content` is a plain textarea field (Twilight custom-component
    fields don't offer a WYSIWYG/HTML format), so line breaks are preserved
    via CSS `white-space: pre-line` rather than an (unsafe/unsupported) `|raw`
    HTML render.
#}
{% if component.content %}
    <section class="section rich-text-block{{ component.center_align ? ' rich-text-block--center' : '' }}">
        <div class="container rich-text-block__inner">
            {% if component.title %}
                <h2 class="section__title">{{ component.title }}</h2>
            {% endif %}
            <p class="rich-text-block__content">{{ component.content }}</p>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endif %}
